{"tid":1545880,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港交所冧機】李小加：系統有bug致休市","createTime":"2019-09-06T05:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T12:03:22.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"06fdf7882ddb71c1a673fb3a3b85e596e0fbafd5","tid":1545880,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZDaSuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZDaSuv.jpg&h=57ae6d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日港交所（0388）交易系統不穩，釀成首次衍生產品盤中收市。港交所行政總裁李小加表示，昨日故障原因為系統軟件出現缺陷（bug），現時連結已正常，所有產品已可交易。但由於現時使用舊版軟件，因此有少部分功能暫時無法使用，但不會影響市場交易。他補充指出，昨日網站不穩是由於受到DDos攻擊，但該攻擊與系統bug無關。"},{"pid":"b9318fd5205690429566bd3d147cbe39dbfa28dd","tid":1545880,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f14afc08a199c6ecec78147838edf1803457e23a","tid":1545880,"uid":182180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"等到20年後先出現既bug"},{"pid":"6f4d0cd83ce7ed3550bd9760907681f5cadfe695","tid":1545880,"uid":31773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"我d錢無bug架"},{"pid":"e97c83105fb3843b0371ada128d9cebe25d6df42","tid":1545880,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"成見事好鬼"},{"pid":"a19187f74a28272a4c10c9f6930772054f435749","tid":1545880,"uid":149215,"like":0,"di